pkcs11-helper -- PKCS#11 simplification.

Copyright (c) 2005-2006 Alon Bar-Lev <alon.barlev@gmail.com>

POSIX
	Dependencies:
	        dl
		threading: (Optional)
			pthread (nptl)
		engine-crypt: (Optional, usually must choose)
			OpenSSL>=0.9.7 || GNUTLS>=1.4.4
		openssl: (Optional)
			OpenSSL>=0.9.7
		doc: (Optional)
			doxygen>=1.4

	Build:
		$ ./configure
		$ make
		$ make install

Cross-MinGW32
	Dependencies:
		man2html
		openssl: (Optional)
			OpenSSL>=0.9.7
		doc: (Optional)
			doxygen>=1.4

	Build:
		w32root=/tmp/w32root

		Without openssl engine:
			./configure --prefix=/ --host=mingw32 --disable-openssl
		With openssl engine:
			./configure --prefix=/ --host=mingw32 \
				PKG_CONFIG=true \
				OPENSSL_CFLAGS="-I${w32root}/include" \
				OPENSSL_LIBS="-L${w32root}/lib -lcrypto"
											
		make
		make install DESTDIR=${w32root}

	Create Microsoft LIB file (Optional):
		[[Must use Microsoft lib utility]]
		lib /def:libpkcs11-helper-1.dll.def \
			/name:libpkcs11-helper-1.dll \
			/out:libpkcs11-helper-1.lib

Native-Cygwin
	Dependencies:
		Same as Cross-MinGW32

	Build:
		w32root=/tmp/w32root

		Without openssl engine:
			./configure --prefix=/ --with-cygwin-native --disable-openssl
		With openssl engine:
			./configure --prefix=/ --with-cygwin-native \
				PKG_CONFIG=true \
				OPENSSL_CFLAGS="-I${w32root}/include" \
				OPENSSL_LIBS="-L${w32root}/lib -lcrypto"
		make
		make install DESTDIR=${w32root}

Visual Studio
	Dependencies:
		None.

	Build:
		cd lib
		nmake -f Makefile.w32-vc

